      "default": "<sub>As you learn about the benefits of tax credits, take a moment to explore our selection of<strong> ENERGY STAR® certified air conditioners.</strong> From<strong> <a href=\"https://dellahome.com/collections/mini-split-ac\" target=\"_self\"><span style=\"color: rgb(9, 99, 241);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(5, 49, 117);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(59, 59, 240);\">ductless mini splits</span></span></span></a></strong> to <strong>heat pumps</strong>, our products are designed to maximize comfort while helping you save on energy bills and qualify for available tax incentives.<br><br>If you have any questions about which systems are eligible or need guidance finding the right fit for your home, our team is here to assist. Feel free to<strong> reach out</strong> anytime for personalized advice and support.</sub>"
